skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill

des: A football minded flash briefing brought to you by the sports loving crew at Buttonpushapps. We used the public RSS feed owned by ESPN to create this briefing skill. It contains the latest news from the world of college football. Enable this skill and include it as part of your daily flash.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
